member.summary:
the DataView property contains the filtered and transformed data records after data binding and all feature transformations
have been applied
///

The difference between compact JSON response and non-compact is that for "compact" mode, JSON is rendered as an array of values, such as
[val1, val2, val3]
while in non-compact mode JSON is rendered as an object with name-value pairs, such as:
{key1: val1, key2: val2, key3: val3 }
